            <path d="M22 12.07C22 6.5 17.52 2 12 2S2 6.5 2 12.07C2 17.1 5.66 21.27 10.44 22v-7.03H7.9v-2.9h2.54V9.84c0-2.52 1.49-3.91 3.78-3.91 1.1 0 2.25.2 2.25.2v2.48H15.2c-1.25 0-1.64.78-1.64 1.58v1.88h2.8l-.45 2.9h-2.35V22C18.34 21.27 22 17.1 22 12.07Z"/>
